      pubDate: '2023-05-16 20:05:17',
      link: 'https://medium.com/xeniasuite/tips-and-tricks-for-hotels-to-boost-direct-bookings-amidst-the-rise-of-online-travel-agencies-64e55ce8eca1?source=rss----fd4140b823ce---4',
      guid: 'https://medium.com/p/64e55ce8eca1',
      author: 'Xenia Suite',
      thumbnail: '',
      description:
        '\n<figure><img alt="" src="https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/700/1*heBgu1doPO8IQvmD9583fQ.jpeg"></figure><p>In 2023 hotels are facing more competition than ever before. With shifting consumer demands and the rise of online travel agencies (OTAs) like Expedia, Booking.com, and Hotels.com, it can be a challenge for hotels to attract and retain customers. But don\u2019t worry, with the right strategy, your hotel can increase direct bookings and avoid paying high commission fees to\u00a0OTAs.</p>\n<h3>User-Friendly Website</h3>\n<p>One of the best ways to boost direct bookings is by having a user-friendly and visually appealing website. A website that\u2019s easy to navigate, quick to load, and optimized for search engines will make it more likely for potential customers to book directly with your hotel. Also, by including high-quality photos and videos of your hotel\u2019s rooms, facilities, and surroundings, you can help customers envision their stay and make a booking decision.</p>\n<h3>Exclusive Deals</h3>\n<p>Another great strategy is to offer exclusive deals and promotions to customers who book directly with your hotel. This could be things like discounted room rates, complimentary breakfast, or late check-out. By offering these incentives, you can encourage customers to book directly and avoid the high commission fees charged by\u00a0OTAs.</p>\n<h3>Incentivising Loyalty</h3>\n<p>Linked to this is direct marketing activity that looks to re-engage past customers. Your past guests are a gold mine when it comes to rebooking. Re-engage past customers using an email marketing campaign with compelling discounts and offers. Also, if you don\u2019t have one, consider launching a loyalty program. Travellers respond well to these programs, and you\u2019ll learn much more about your best guest profiles. Your loyalty programs don\u2019t have to be complicated, with points and redemptions\u200a\u2014\u200ait could be as simple as promising \u201cMembers Only\u201d\u00a0rates.</p>\n<h3>Social Media</h3>\n<p>Social media is also a powerful tool that hotels can use to increase direct bookings. By having a presence on platforms like Facebook, Instagram, and Twitter, hotels can connect with potential customers, share information about their hotel, and offer promotions and deals. Additionally, by leveraging user-generated content, hotels can showcase positive reviews and experiences of their guests which can help build trust and credibility.</p>\n<h3>Personalise the guest experience</h3>\n<p>Guest profiles within PMS systems like <a href="https://www.xeniasuite.co.nz/">Xenia Suite</a> can contain detailed information, such as birthdays, anniversaries, and special requests. You can use this information with guest messaging software to build guest relationships and offer personalized services, special discounts, and deals during their\u00a0stay.</p>\n<p>For instance, say one of your guests recently visited your property for an anniversary trip, and they noted that they have an allergy to something like gluten. Imagine the guest\u2019s reaction if you send them a personalised direct message (possible through <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=golq8LGkaKg">Xenia Suite\u2019s Guest App</a>) informing them that your restaurant has recently expanded its gluten-free options and are offering their room at a discounted rate for their upcoming anniversary. Personalised service creates lasting customer loyalty and encourages repeat visits and direct bookings. Better yet, you can get started start away with Xenia Suite\u2019s end-to-end hotel software.</p>\n<a href="https://medium.com/media/c60b92a7cd25e50c5fa86b016fad3f61/href">https://medium.com/media/c60b92a7cd25e50c5fa86b016fad3f61/href</a><p>By implementing these strategies, your hotel can increase direct bookings and avoid paying high commission fees to OTAs. Happy\u00a0booking!</p>\n<p><strong>Contact us today to schedule a consultation and learn how </strong><a href="https://www.xeniasuite.co.nz/"><strong>Xenia Suite\u2019s end-to-end hotel management software</strong></a><strong> can help you increase direct bookings, improve operational efficiency, and so much more. Don\u2019t miss out on this opportunity to take your hotel to the next\u00a0level!</strong></p>\n<img src="https://medium.com/_/stat?event=post.clientViewed&amp;referrerSource=full_rss&amp;postId=64e55ce8eca1" width="1" height="1" alt=""><hr>\n<p><a href="https://medium.com/xeniasuite/tips-and-tricks-for-hotels-to-boost-direct-bookings-amidst-the-rise-of-online-travel-agencies-64e55ce8eca1">Tips and Tricks for Hotels to Boost Direct Bookings Amidst the Rise of Online Travel Agencies</a> was originally published in <a href="https://medium.com/xeniasuite">xeniasuite</a> on Medium, where people are continuing the conversation by highlighting and responding to this story.</p>\n',
